The head of this morning star appears to be forged from unbreakable ice-blue crystal. The handle is chill to the touch, and the wielder is surrounded by a soothing nimbus of cool air which protects against even magical fire.
Ice Star
Lysanna
A swirl of a vortex adorns the floor. Its meaning is not known to you.
Cold, frosty air emanates from this massive crystal of ice. Its surface looks so cold that putting your tongue to it would be highly inadvisable.
